# Repo-wide safety net for runtime SQLite database files.
# Backend-specific rules also live in backend/.gitignore; these repeat them at
# the repository root so the backend/-prefixed patterns take effect too, and so
# any DB file created elsewhere in the tree is caught.
*.db
*.db-shm
*.db-wal
replywise.db
backend/replywise.db
backend/*.db
backend/*.db-shm
backend/*.db-wal
